  <entry>
    <title>使用Hexo搭建属于你自己的博客</title>
    <link href="/posts/Hexo-Fluid-Blog/"/>
    <url>/posts/Hexo-Fluid-Blog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>欢迎来到 <a href="https://blog.minestart.cn/">MineStart’s Blog</a>，为您带来有用且免费的经验教学!<br>Hexo博客是我一步一步摸索过来的，期间我找了很多博主的教程，结合起来，就有了今天的教程！</p></blockquote><h1 id="前提"><a href="#前提" class="headerlink" title="前提"></a>前提</h1><p>相信大家对于博客这个东西不陌生吧，我身边的朋友包括我同学都有属于他们自己的博客</p><ul><li><a href="https://msdnicrosoft.cn/">MSDNicrosoft ‘s Blog</a></li><li><a href="https://guaijie.ml/">GuaiJie’s Blog</a></li><li><a href="https://mintimate.cn/">Mintimate’s Blog</a></li></ul><p>等等(在我的友情链接里owo)</p><p>市面上的博客有很多博客，这里我收集了一些常用的博客(仅针对个人意见！！)</p><ul><li><a href="https://wordpress.com/">WordPress</a><blockquote><p>优点：功能强大、扩展性强、对seo搜索引擎友好、适合DIY<br>缺点：不能安装太多插件、备份和网站转移比较繁琐，需要涉及到数据库!</p></blockquote></li><li><a href="http://typecho.org/">Typecho</a><blockquote><p>优点： 容易上手，对小白友好、简单快速的博客平台<br>缺点： 主题模板少</p></blockquote></li><li><a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a><blockquote><p>优点：美观简洁，主题模板多<br>缺点：暂时没有qaq</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><strong>那我们今天使用Hexo来搭建一个属于你自己的Blog(doge)</strong></p><h1 id="使用视频辅助搭建"><a href="#使用视频辅助搭建" class="headerlink" title="使用视频辅助搭建"></a>使用视频辅助搭建</h1><h1 id="准备环境"><a href="#准备环境" class="headerlink" title="准备环境"></a>准备环境</h1><p>我这里选择的是Windows环境，如果你不是Windows环境的观众请移步至 <a href="https://www.mintimate.cn/2020/03/19/hexo/#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B">Mintimate’s Blog</a></p><h2 id="下载安装所需文件"><a href="#下载安装所需文件" class="headerlink" title="下载安装所需文件"></a>下载安装所需文件</h2><ul><li><a href="https://nodejs.org/">Node.js</a></li><li><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">Git</a> or <a href="https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/git-for-windows/">淘宝 Git for Windows</a></li><li><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/Download">VSCode</a></li></ul><p>这边最好选择个梯子，方便我们去下载东西(bushi</p><p><strong>下载完记得安装哦~</strong></p><h2 id="修改npm下载源"><a href="#修改npm下载源" class="headerlink" title="修改npm下载源"></a>修改npm下载源</h2><p><strong>在<code>桌面</code>-<code>鼠标右键</code>-<code>找到&quot;Git Bash Here&quot;</code>，点击<code>&quot;Git Bash Here&quot;</code></strong></p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino">npm config set registry https:<span class="hljs-comment">//registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着输入以下代码来验证是否安装成功</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">npm<span class="hljs-built_in"> config </span><span class="hljs-built_in">get</span> registry<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p align="center">  <img alt="修改成功" src="/img/img-2/1.png" width="650"></p><blockquote><p><strong>注：如果想还原npm仓库地址，只需再把地址配置成npm镜像就可以了</strong></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino">npm config set registry https:<span class="hljs-comment">//registry.npmjs.org/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="部署Hexo到本地"><a href="#部署Hexo到本地" class="headerlink" title="部署Hexo到本地"></a>部署Hexo到本地</h1><h2 id="安装Hexo框架"><a href="#安装Hexo框架" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo框架"></a>安装Hexo框架</h2><blockquote><p><strong>可按照 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">Hexo 官方文档</a> 来安装</strong></p></blockquote><p><strong>在桌面找个地方新建文件夹，统一取名为<code>&quot;Blog&quot;</code>，不建议使用中文名称，不然后面报错你都不知道怎么死的qaq</strong></p><p align="center">  <img alt="新建文件夹" src="/img/img-2/2.png"></p><p>统一取名为”Blog”，方便以后部署</p><p align="center">  <img alt="统一重命名为'Blog'" src="/img/img-2/3.png"></p><p>进入<code>&quot;Blog&quot;</code>文件夹-<code>鼠标右键</code>-点击<code>&quot;Git Bash Here&quot;</code></p><p align="center">  <img alt="点击'Git Bash Here'" src="/img/img-2/4.png"></p><p>然后在Git窗口输入安装Hexo博客指令</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">npm install -g hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安装Hexo后输入新建博客文件夹</strong></p><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">init</span> blog<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着进入<code>&quot;Blog&quot;</code>文件夹</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> Blog<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动Hexo博客</p><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs axapta">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">server</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-success">            <p><strong>hexo server 简写为hexo s</strong></p>          </div><h2 id="安装Hexo-Fluid主题"><a href="#安装Hexo-Fluid主题" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo-Fluid主题"></a>安装Hexo-Fluid主题</h2><blockquote><p><strong>可按照 <a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/">Hexo-Fluid 官方文档</a> 来安装</strong></p></blockquote><p>下载 <a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid/releases">最新 release 版本</a> 解压到 /Blog/themes 目录，并将解压出的文件夹重命名为 <code>fluid</code>。</p><p>然后在博客目录下创建 <code>_config.fluid.yml</code>，将主题的 <a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid/blob/master/_config.yml">_config.yml</a> 内容复制进去。</p><h2 id="修改Hexo主题为Fluid主题"><a href="#修改Hexo主题为Fluid主题" class="headerlink" title="修改Hexo主题为Fluid主题"></a>修改Hexo主题为Fluid主题</h2><p>使用VScode打开<code>/blog/blog/_config.yml</code>文件</p><p align="center">  <img alt="打开'_config.yml'文件" src="/img/img-2/5.png"></p><p>然后在第100行左右找到<code>theme</code> ，把<code>landscape</code>改为<code>Fluid</code></p><p align="center">  <img alt="修改前" src="/img/img-2/6-1.png"></p><p align="center">  <img alt="修改后" src="/img/img-2/6-2.png"></p><div class="note note-warning">            <p><strong>如果是其他主题，就把<code>Fluid</code>替换为你的主题的名字</strong></p><p>e.g. 假如我要安装的主题是 <code>NexT</code> ，那我要把<code>Fluid</code>改为<code>NexT</code></p>          </div><blockquote><p><strong>别忘记了Ctrl+S保存下哦~~</strong></p></blockquote><h1 id="美化Hexo-Fluid主题"><a href="#美化Hexo-Fluid主题" class="headerlink" title="美化Hexo-Fluid主题"></a>美化Hexo-Fluid主题</h1><p>这里可以跳过，也可以按照教程一步一步做下去</p><h2 id="修改语言"><a href="#修改语言" class="headerlink" title="修改语言"></a>修改语言</h2><p>Hexo默认语言为<code>en_US</code>，所以我们需要把语言改为中文</p><p>使用VSCode打开博客下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件</p><p align="center">  <img alt="打开'_config.yml'文件" src="/img/img-2/5.png"></p><p>在第11行左右找到<code>language</code> ，把<code>en</code>改为<code>zh-CN</code>或<code>zh-Hans</code></p><p align="center">  <img alt="修改前" src="/img/img-2/7-1.png"></p><p align="center">  <img alt="修改后" src="/img/img-2/7-2.png"></p><h2 id="修改主题配色"><a href="#修改主题配色" class="headerlink" title="修改主题配色"></a>修改主题配色</h2><p>我个人觉得主题的 明/暗 配色已经很不错了，不需要改。 如果需要改请往下看qaq</p><p>打开主题下的<code>_config.fluid.yml</code>文件</p><p>找到<code>Color</code></p><p align="center">  <img alt="主题配色" src="/img/img-2/8.png"></p<p>可以去 <a href="https://www.webdesignrankings.com/resources/lolcolors/">Color选择</a> 获得启发</p><p>都是官方的内容，我就不唠叨了</p><h2 id="关于页、友情链接、404页"><a href="#关于页、友情链接、404页" class="headerlink" title="关于页、友情链接、404页"></a>关于页、友情链接、404页</h2><h3 id="创建「关于页」"><a href="#创建「关于页」" class="headerlink" title="创建「关于页」"></a>创建「关于页」</h3><p>回到博客目录-<code>鼠标右键</code>-找到<code>Git Bash Here</code></p><p align="center">  <img alt="打开 Git Bash" src="/img/img-2/9.png"></p<p>输入</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">page</span> about<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p align="center">  <img alt="创建关于页" src="/img/img-2/10.png"></p<p>创建成功后，编辑博客目录下 <code>/source/about/index.md</code>，添加 <code>layout</code> 属性。</p><p>修改后的文件示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">about</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2021-10-30 00:41:25</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span> <span class="hljs-string">about</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-string">这里写关于页的正文，支持</span> <span class="hljs-string">Markdown,</span> <span class="hljs-string">HTML</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建「友情链接」"><a href="#创建「友情链接」" class="headerlink" title="创建「友情链接」"></a>创建「友情链接」</h3><p>打开博客下的<code>_config.fluid.yml</code></p><p>找到<code>Links Page</code> （如果找不到可以Ctrl+F搜索)</p><h3 id="创建「404页」"><a href="#创建「404页」" class="headerlink" title="创建「404页」"></a>创建「404页」</h3><p>回到博客目录-<code>鼠标右键</code>-找到<code>Git Bash Here</code></p><p align="center">  <img alt="打开 Git Bash" src="/img/img-2/9.png"></p<p>输入</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">page</span> <span class="hljs-number">404</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p align="center">  <img alt="创建关于页" src="/img/img-2/11.png"></p<p>创建成功后，编辑博客目录下 <code>/source/404/index.md</code>，添加 <code>layout</code> 属性。</p><p>修改后的文件示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-number">404</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2021-10-30 00:41:25</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span> <span class="hljs-number">404</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加页脚"><a href="#添加页脚" class="headerlink" title="添加页脚"></a>添加页脚</h2><h3 id="博客运行时间"><a href="#博客运行时间" class="headerlink" title="博客运行时间"></a>博客运行时间</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;span&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text/javascript&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"></span><br><span class="language-javascript">        <span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">runtime</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            X = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Date</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;10/12/2021 20:47:00&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            Y = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Date</span>();</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            T = (Y.<span class="hljs-title function_">getTime</span>()-X.<span class="hljs-title function_">getTime</span>());</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            M = <span class="hljs-number">24</span>*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>*<span class="hljs-number">1000</span>;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            a = T/M;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            A = <span class="hljs-title class_">Math</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">floor</span>(a);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            b = (a-A)*<span class="hljs-number">24</span>;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            B = <span class="hljs-title class_">Math</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">floor</span>(b);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            c = (b-B)*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            C = <span class="hljs-title class_">Math</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">floor</span>((b-B)*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            D = <span class="hljs-title class_">Math</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">floor</span>((c-C)*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            span.<span class="hljs-property">innerHTML</span> = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;本站不正常运行了: &quot;</span>+A+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;天&quot;</span>+B+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;小时&quot;</span>+C+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;分&quot;</span>+D+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;秒&quot;</span></span><br><span class="language-javascript">        &#125;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">        <span class="hljs-built_in">setInterval</span>(runtime, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">    </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="MySSL安全印章"><a href="#MySSL安全印章" class="headerlink" title="MySSL安全印章"></a>MySSL安全印章</h3><p>这个嘛，就是去 <a href="https://myssl.com/">MySSL</a> 验证你的网站是否安全， 然后把<code>MySSL</code>的安全印章放到自己博客的页脚</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;cc-myssl-id&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://static.myssl.com/res/images/myssl-id3.png&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">onclick</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;pic()&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">alt</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;max-height:50px;display:block;margin:0 auto&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"></span><br><span class="language-javascript">        <span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">pic</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)</span><br><span class="language-javascript">        &#123;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            <span class="hljs-variable language_">window</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://myssl.com/seal/detail?domain=yourdomain&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;_blank&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;left=pixels,location=yes,width=460,height=869&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">        &#125;      </span><br><span class="language-javascript">    </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-warning">            <p>在<code>window.open(&quot;https://myssl.com/seal/detail?domain=yourdomain&quot;, &quot;_blank&quot;, &quot;left=pixels,location=yes,width=460,height=869&quot;);</code>中</p><p><strong><code>domain=yourdomain</code>需要把你的域名填上去(前提是要在MySSL上验证过才能)</strong></p><p>e.g. 比如我的域名为blog.xx.cn 我需要把<code>domain=blog.xx.cn</code>替换掉<code>yourdomain</code></p>          </div><h3 id="添加插件"><a href="#添加插件" class="headerlink" title="添加插件"></a>添加插件</h3><h3 id="添加js和css脚本"><a href="#添加js和css脚本" class="headerlink" title="添加js和css脚本"></a>添加js和css脚本</h3><h1 id="部署到远程服务器"><a href="#部署到远程服务器" class="headerlink" title="部署到远程服务器"></a>部署到远程服务器</h1><h2 id="部署到个人Server"><a href="#部署到个人Server" class="headerlink" title="部署到个人Server"></a>部署到个人Server</h2><h2 id="部署到静态托管"><a href="#部署到静态托管" class="headerlink" title="部署到静态托管"></a>部署到静态托管</h2><h3 id="Github"><a href="#Github" class="headerlink" title="Github"></a>Github</h3><h3 id="Coding"><a href="#Coding" class="headerlink" title="Coding"></a>Coding</h3><h1 id="Q-amp-A（问与答）"><a href="#Q-amp-A（问与答）" class="headerlink" title="Q&amp;A（问与答）"></a>Q&amp;A（问与答）</h1><h1 id="结尾"><a href="#结尾" class="headerlink" title="结尾"></a>结尾</h1>]]></content>
    
    
